Package: boloot-calendar
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         boloot-calendar-core,
         boloot-calendar-gnome
Description: Persian calendar system for Linux
 BOLOOT Persian Calendar integrates Jalali calendar, prayer times,
 and official holidays for Iran, Afghanistan, and Tajikistan.

