Recommends: boloot-calendar-gnome
Description: BOLOOT Persian Calendar core daemon and data
 Core D-Bus service, CLI tool, GTK4 settings app, locale data,
 holiday database, KDE plasmoid, and XFCE helper.

Package: boloot-calendar-gnome
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         boloot-calendar-core,
         gnome-shell (>= 45),
         fonts-vazirmatn | fonts-vazir
Description: GNOME Shell extension for BOLOOT Persian Calendar
 Displays Persian date and prayer times in the GNOME top bar.
